{"id":284219,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-广州举牌哥刘辉第四次遭广东警方遣/","date":"2013-03-15T09:46:09Z","modified":"2013-03-15T09:46:09Z","title":"维权网 | 广州“举牌哥”刘辉第四次遭广东警方遣返陕西老家（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员赵小明报道）因连续在广州街头举牌呼吁自由民主的刘辉被人们成为“举牌哥”。他于</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日</span><span>星期四上午被广州国保跟踪扣押，随后将其强行遣返陕西老家。刘辉与</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日夜回到西安。刘辉是广州警方在拘押了打出“打倒共产党，打倒独裁专政”的举牌勇士黄文勋后，打击的又一位举牌要求自由民主的勇士。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘辉最近又在广州街头连续两次举起“打倒共产党独裁，建立民主，我是刘辉”以及“誓死反共，解放人民，民主自由，我是刘辉”的横幅，后遭到广州警方跟踪扣押，这是他第四次遭广东警方遣返陕西老家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘辉曾于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>在广州繁华市区上下九路举着“反对独裁，自由民主”牌子个体游行。刘辉公开打出这样的横幅口号，当时在国内外引起了极大关注。随后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>他被广州警方拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>天，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日</span><span>释放后被遣返回老家陕西。此事本网曾第一时间予以报道。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘辉是一名具有自由民主信念的公民，他用自己力所能及的行动公开表达自己的信念，所作所为完全受宪法的保护。广东警方一而再、再而三，三而四地践踏刘辉的基本人权，实际上是对中国宪法的肆意践踏。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘辉，男，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">35</span><span>岁，生于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1978</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>。陕西省黄陵县店头镇人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1998</span><span>年就来到广东谋生，至今已经</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>年了。刘辉仅仅因为举起“反对独裁，自由民主”的牌子而遭受广东警方连续不断的迫害，四次被遣返回老家，给自己的生活带来了极大的困扰。对于刘辉先生的情况，本网将持续关注。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-M4y1sQv5RGg/UUKIAkzz9wI/AAAAAAAAe2E/y0_8sD7uZw0/s1600/2013-03-15+10.17.32.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-M4y1sQv5RGg/UUKIAkzz9wI/AAAAAAAAe2E/y0_8sD7uZw0/s400/2013-03-15+10.17.32.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-VLDgXWv-HbE/UUKIFQLoeuI/AAAAAAAAe2M/pxqtlIoihUw/s1600/1302210306492604.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-VLDgXWv-HbE/UUKIFQLoeuI/AAAAAAAAe2M/pxqtlIoihUw/s400/1302210306492604.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-A0GOGuqzDmk/UUKIH1Ue28I/AAAAAAAAe2U/km6o79G-d8E/s1600/DSC_0000093.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-A0GOGuqzDmk/UUKIH1Ue28I/AAAAAAAAe2U/km6o79G-d8E/s400/DSC_0000093.jpg\" width=\"300\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}